Ultima Missions

Ultima missions may be attempted after having all quests cleared to up to tier 5 in Dimensions' End: Entropy.


Ultima Mission Eligibility

Characters for whom crystal strength level 90 has been unlocked will be given the following missions:
・Enhance target ally to crystal strength level 90
・Clear eligible LUFENIA quest with target ally in the party

Clearing each mission will reward providence cores used to cast and sublimate ultima weapons.

Refer to the game guide below for more details on ultima weapons.

Ultima Weapons



Ultima Mission Quests

The quests eligible for clearing the mission "Clear eligible LUFENIA quest with target ally in the party" can be seen with the Quests or Embark buttons.

*Any quest with a difficulty level of "LUFENIA" in the name is initially eligible.
*Co-op quests are ineligible.

One quest may be used to clear three allies' ultima missions.

Once three allies' missions have been cleared with a particular quest, a different quest must be used for further allies.



The remaining number of allies a quest can support is displayed on the Ultima Mission Quest and party formation screens.

Recommended parties and tips for clearing ultima mission quests are also available.

Use this information to the fullest to clear every ally's ultima mission!


*Recommended parties suggest combinations of allies that should make it easier to clear the given quest, but allies other than those recommended may also be used to clear the quest and their respective ultima missions.
